 <name>GChemPaint</name>
 <summary>Draw and display 2D chemical structures</summary>
 <description>
  <p>
    GChemPaint is an editor for 2D chemical structures. It can display not only
	molecules but also reactions and more. It is able to export structures to
	various file formats as well to some 3D viewers. It also give access to
	online databases.
  </p>
  <p>
    GChemPaint is part of the GNOME Chemistry Utils set of chemistry related
    programs.
  </p>
 </description>
